{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban publishing information about people accused of crimes until proven guilty",
        "additional_details": "People arrested for crimes may be innocent. I think their lives could be ruined if information is published about them. Their family and children could also be put in danger.",
        "background": "I want the government to prevent the names and photos of people accused of crimes from being released until they are proven guilty. I do not think that newspapers should be allowed to put people\u2019s jobs and safety at risk.",
